high_descs: Face the sink to the left of the toilet.
Open the right side of the under-sink cabinet and take out a purple cloth, then close the cabinet.
Take the purple cloth to the sink.
Wash the purple cloth in the sink.
Carry the purple cloth to the toilet on your right.
Lay the purple cloth on top of the toilet tank cover.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean purple cloth on the lid of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn around, take a step forward and then turn right to face the sink
Open the right cabinet door below the sink and grab a cloth.
Raise the cloth to the sink.
Rinse the cloth in the sink and then remove it.
Turn around and turn left, then walk towards the bath tub and turn left towards the toilet.
Place the cloth on top of the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean cloth on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward towards the wall, then turn right and face the sink.
Open cabinet beneath the sink closest to the toilet, take the dirty cloth and then close the cabinet.
Move up to the sink counter.
Place the dirty cloth in the sink, turn on both faucets, turn off both faucets, then pick up the cloth.
Turn right and move to the bath tub then turn left and move to the bath towel and then turn left and face the toilet.
Place the cloth on the top of the toilet cistern to the left of the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean cloth on top of the toilet cistern.
